3
00:00:03,879 --> 00:00:05,080
It's all Mason's doing.

4
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:07,139
They were worth some project.

5
00:00:07,139 --> 00:00:08,259
Someone had to swim wrong.

6
00:00:08,259 --> 00:00:10,619
