9
00:00:16,179 --> 00:00:30,329
He doesn't know, but even I met him.

10
00:00:30,329 --> 00:00:32,070
Evil, disgusting bastard.

11
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:34,149
Chloe, what are you doing here?

12
00:00:34,149 --> 00:00:35,829
I don't even care that you cheated on me

13
00:00:35,829 --> 00:00:37,310
