14
00:00:37,310 --> 00:00:38,149
None of that matters.

15
00:00:38,149 --> 00:00:39,070
What does matter?

16
00:00:39,070 --> 00:00:41,549
Very much to me, Mason is what you're doing to my father.

17
00:00:41,549 --> 00:00:43,070
In every business venture, there's

18
00:00:43,070 --> 00:00:44,390
